Package view

Class GraphicalSegment

  • java.lang.Object
    • view.GraphicalSegment
  • public class GraphicalSegment
extends java.lang.Object
    Graphical representation for the map of all the segments. Highlighted or not. The segments can be highlighted to represent the tour.
